489
00:34:26,742 --> 00:34:30,642
<i>Que salvou</i>

490
00:34:30,643 --> 00:34:33,943
<i>Um miserável...</i>

491
00:34:47,981 --> 00:34:49,983
Meu Deus!

492
00:34:58,106 --> 00:34:59,790
Liguem para a emergência!

493
00:34:59,791 --> 00:35:01,291
Reverendo Holt.

494
00:35:02,596 --> 00:35:04,595
É a dra. Lynn Stewart.

495
00:35:04,596 --> 00:35:07,098
